4. Direct links to your email and social media accounts.
5. Display the current date and time by default.
6. New note feature to jot down tasks.
7. Quick links to frequently visited sites.
8. Simplified access to your bookmarks.

12. Streamlined social media sharing.
13. One-click download of wallpapers.
